mainHero.title: LaLa
mainHero.subtitle: Photo Booth
mainHero.description: Capture the joy of the moment with our digital Photo Booth experience in Tacoma, WA. Elevate your events with fun and memorable snapshots, offering a unique blend of technology and nostalgia. Perfect for weddings, parties, and corporate gatherings, our Photo Booth adds a touch of excitement to every occasion. Book us now to turn your special moments into timeless memories!

items.title: What types of events do your photo booths cater to?
items.description: We cater to all types of events like weddings, birthday parties, cooperate events and much more.

items.title: Can I customize the photo booth experience for my specific event theme?
items.description: Yes! We edit and customize the border and digital photo strip to your event.

items.title: What features and props are included in your photo booth packages?
items.description: Regular props are included in the package, if you want props to fit your theme there is an extra cost.

items.title: Can the Photo Booth be used outdoors?
items.description: Yes the Photo Booth can be used outdoors!

features.title: Who am I?
features.subtitle: Alahnna Connolly
features.description: A recent graduate of Central Washington University with a degree in Public Relations and a minor in Marketing. While completing my studies in 2023, I founded my Photo Booth business in late 2021, driven by my passion for creating memorable experiences. Having successfully executed over 30 events, I am dedicated to blending creativity and professionalism to add a touch of fun to every occasion. Let's capture your moments in style with my Photo Booth services!

items.name: All Packages Include
features: Text/Email Of All Photos After Event
